<settings>
    <!-- GENERATED: HYBRID model. Each slot carries only Name and Dose; the
         schedule (times, days, reminders on/off) is set on the watch under
         Medications. Keeping phone settings to two small fields per slot lets
         all 18 slots save in a single sync, under Garmin's ~8 KB cap.
         Leave a slot's Name blank to disable/delete that medication. -->

